<commentary>madarthaṃ prasthitasya te pathikāṅganājanāśvāsam amānuṣaṅgikaṃ phalam ity āha—tvām iti || pavanapadavīm ākāśam ārūḍhaṃ tvām | panthānaṃ gacchanti te pathikāḥ || "pathaḥ ṣkan" iti ṣkanpratyayaḥ || teṣāṃ vanitāḥ proṣitabhartṛkāḥ| pratyayāt priyāgamanaviśvāsāt || "pratyayo 'dhīnaśapathajñānaviśvāsahetuṣu" ity amaraḥ || āśvasyatyāḥ viśvasitāḥ || śvasidhātoḥ śatrantāt "ugitaś ca" iti ṅīp | tathodgṛhītālakāntā dṛṣṭiprasārārtham unnamayya dhṛtālakāgrāḥ satyaḥ prekṣiṣyante | atyutkaṇṭhatayā drakṣyantīty arthaḥ || madāgamanena pathikāḥ katham āgamiṣyantīty atrāha—tathā hi | tvayi saṃnaddhe vyāpṛte sati viraheṇa vidhurāṃ vivaśāṃ jāyāṃ ka upekṣeta | na ko 'pīty arthaḥ | anyo 'pi madvyatirikto 'pi yo jano 'ham iva parādhīnavṛttiḥ parāyattajīvanako na syāt | svatantras tu na ko 'py upekṣeteti bhāvaḥ || atrārthāntaranyāso 'laṅkāraḥ | tad uktam—"kāryakāraṇasāmānyaviśeṣāṇāṃ parasparam | samarthanaṃ yatra so 'rthāntaragyāsa udāhṛtaḥ ||" iti lakṣaṇāt ||</commentary>

nimittāny api te śubhāni dṛśyanta ity āha-mandaṃ mandam iti || anukūlaḥ pavano vāyustvāṃ manda mandam | atimandam ity arthaḥ || atra kathañcid vīpsāyām eva dviruktir nirvāhyā | "prakāre guṇavacanasya" ity etad āśrayaṇe tu karmadhārayavad bhāve subluki mandamandam iti syāt | tad evāha vāmanaḥ-"mandamandam ity atra prakārārthe dvirbhāvaḥ" iti | yathā sadṛśam | bhāviphalānurūpam ity arthaḥ || "yathā | sādṛśyayogyatvavīpsārthānatikrame" iti yādavaḥ || nudati prerayati | ayaṃ sagandhaḥ sagarvaḥ | sambandhīti kecit || "gandho gandhaka āmode leśe sambandhagarvayoḥ" ity ubhayatrāpi viśvaḥ || te tava vāmo vāmabhāgasthaḥ || "vāmas tu vakre ramye syāt savye vāmagate 'pi ca" iti śabdārṇave || cātakaḥ pakṣiviśeṣaś ca madhuraṃ śrāvyaṃ nadati vyāharati || idaṃ nimittadvayaṃ vartate | vartiṣyate cāparaṃ nimittam ity āha—garbheti || garbhaḥ kukṣistho jantuḥ || "garbhopakārake hy agnau sukhe panasakaṇṭake |
